DISCLAIMER: This project provides educational information and practice support
templates grounded in published model standards for mediation. It does not
constitute legal advice, therapy, or a substitute for professional judgment.
The model standards referenced herein are published by AFCC, ABA, AAA, and ACR.
This project provides educational commentary, implementation guidance, and
practice templates — it does not reproduce the full text of the standards.
Mediators should obtain and review the original standards from the issuing
organizations.
